<br />\n五毛居心 路人皆見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"咪話自己人各有各做<br />\n唔一定做呢樣就唔做得個樣嘅姐<br />\n咁既話唔好清算囉 由得佢繼續爆手足資料囉<br />\n一黎就話人5毛，咁我話你係bonnie tong本人得唔得呀？？？"},{"pid":"2788dc78ff31f1dd5a4b15d327427d0c3adcb00c","tid":1765833,"uid":323591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a14aec7fd50573590d57f0c65d0d0501ecb838a","tid":1765833,"uid":295075,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2e92a0bde4147369cc3bb9e0cbe876c316830e7","tid":1765833,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:52:59.000Z","msg":"連登仔相信一張員工證<br />\n唔信big 4<br />\n講出去都俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"E單野都幾煩 傳左咁耐 交代完又唔信 好似無限loop"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"咁黑警夠日日出黎交代佢地點樣打人呀，推呀婆落地係合情合理合法啦，係咪交代完就要信呀？？？？"},{"pid":"c4cab6c36b3acc7d61baafeda45d495568e9f7c2","tid":1765833,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2788dc78ff31f1dd5a4b15d327427d0c3adcb00c","tid":1765833,"uid":323591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a14aec7fd50573590d57f0c65d0d0501ecb838a","tid":1765833,"uid":295075,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2e92a0bde4147369cc3bb9e0cbe876c316830e7","tid":1765833,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:52:59.000Z","msg":"連登仔相信一張員工證<br />\n唔信big 4<br />\n講出去都俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"E單野都幾煩 傳左咁耐 交代完又唔信 好似無限loop"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"咁黑警夠日日出黎交代佢地點樣打人呀，推呀婆落地係合情合理合法啦，係咪交代完就要信呀？？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"哦 即係渣打回應 你唔信<br />\n德勤報告你唔信<br />\n咁你既然咩都唔信 你又會信張員工證嘅文嘅？<br />\n到真係外國都話佢係冇事，你咪又係會唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"05eac8a0d59a57d5f26c4cb8cc81f506efe2457b","tid":1765833,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:30:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03028030c9140349d83ee3cb3b8aad31d462ae62","tid":1765833,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"525d58e88f95b8280dfd98846ea6af56e829b684","tid":1765833,"uid":323591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"人渣警嫂Bonnie Tong唐曉華將手足資料起底直接交比做東九龍反黑組警察老公事件，由10月發生到而家都好似無咩進展咁，Bonnie Tong仲未比人抄，而渣打亦都就咁求其話搵左獨立第三方顧問去調查就當無左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[拋磚引玉] 其實渣打八婆Bonnie Tong單野可唔可以向歐盟申訴？</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1762624\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1762624</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我朋友都諗到可以用GDPR去投訴，呢個post我係代佢出，希望可以多啲人一齊send個email，用連登力量令佢收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面個post嘅樓主其實都解釋得好清楚，呢到簡單講小小，GDPR全寫係General Data Protection Regulation，係歐盟法規《一般資料保護規例》<br />\n<br />\n以下係wiki搵到嘅簡介：<br />\nGDPR是在歐盟法律中對所有歐盟個人關於數據保護和專有的規範，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">涉及到歐洲 境外的個人資料出口。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n換言之，即係話渣打疑似縱容及包疪員工盜用客戶資料，而渣打客戶當中一定有EU citizens，歐盟委員會亦有機會會介入罰款渣打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以幫下手每人Send個email去比渣打迫佢2個星期內要對公眾交代，否則直接向歐盟委員會申訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*******************************************************<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncustomer.care@sc.com<br />\n<br />\nSubject: Potential Breach of GDPR&nbsp;<br />\n***<br />\nTo whom it may concern,<br />\n<br />\nIt has come to my attention that there are allegations against one of your employees (Bonnie Tong from the Tsing Yi Branch) who allegedly stole client's personal information and leaked the information to her police officer husband. While I understand your bank has appointed a third party to perform investigation into these allegations, I wish to bring your attention to the potential breach of General Data Protection Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (GDPR) by your bank. As an international bank, I am certain Standard Chartered serves clients of different nationalities, including EU citizens. If the allegations against Ms. Tong are true, it is possible that she had stolen and leaked the personal information of your clients who are EU citizens. This is a direct breach of the GDPR which could result in a fine of up to&nbsp;&euro;20 million, or 4% of the firm&rsquo;s worldwide annual revenue from the preceding financial year, whichever amount is higher.&nbsp;I strongly advise you to discuss with your internal legal team the consequences of a breach of the GDPR rule.<br />\n<br />\nIn a competitive and saturated consumer market that is Hong Kong, many of us are customers of your bank who have a genuine concern and worry about the lack of disciplinary action following such a gross breach of our privacy, especially in such tumultuous times. &nbsp;Trust that your bank will deal with this adequately given the stakes involved.<br />\n<br />\nGiven the seriousness of the allegations involved in this incident, I demand a response from you within 14 days failing which I have no choice but to bring these to the attention of the EU Commission.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\nXX"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:16:39.000Z","msg":"我想知EU有冇覆巴打你呀？呢條戰線好似冇乜消息"},{"pid":"fd4692230d7b8dc7bf54b4e8f9cd8b0a00a486d2","tid":1765833,"uid":318497,"like