sonal information of your clients who are EU citizens. This is a direct breach of the GDPR which could result in a fine of up to&nbsp;&euro;20 million, or 4% of the firm&rsquo;s worldwide annual revenue from the preceding financial year, whichever amount is higher.&nbsp;I strongly advise you to discuss with your internal legal team the consequences of a breach of the GDPR rule.<br />\n<br />\nIn a competitive and saturated consumer market that is Hong Kong, many of us are customers of your bank who have a genuine concern and worry about the lack of disciplinary action following such a gross breach of our privacy, especially in such tumultuous times. &nbsp;Trust that your bank will deal with this adequately given the stakes involved.<br />\n<br />\nGiven the seriousness of the allegations involved in this incident, I demand a response from you within 14 days failing which I have no choice but to bring these to the attention of the EU Commission.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\nXX"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e81cb0a0faa16d624dda30600b54ee7807fbf55","tid":1765833,"uid":179334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"唔可以放過呢個臭閪"},{"pid":"637a3d07e710f7df95800263603e8441042c5c6e","tid":1765833,"uid":179334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"佢害撚左好多手足"},{"pid":"e070579bd2bba8ded45d043212a4041443502ad5","tid":1765833,"uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d72fc02ac8c30d241b425eb36d63acd9c8d8203","tid":1765833,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:12:56.000Z","msg":"寄"},{"pid":"c3e3ef4ce646b944dac7162766ab0195145f7fee","tid":1765833,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:15:31.000Z","msg":"呢d人唔可以